{"ts":"2026-06-22T11:07:27.740Z","author":"codex-sdk-cli-continuation","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-22T11:07:27.740Z","author":"codex-sdk-cli-continuation","text":"Review follow-up: Gemini correctly pointed out the stronger fix belongs in src/core/telemetry/runtime.ts. Updated scheduleTelemetryFlush to spawn the detached worker with cwd=os.tmpdir(), then restored the integration test to run the foreground CLI from the sandbox temp root and removed redundant fs.rm native retries."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-22T11:07:27.740Z"}],"before_hash":"88f36dac4fcd18fb78eec51c66b6dc4998d6e56f8b8bb02d80a637f3b7a0cdce","after_hash":"fbc430cddb487e37ae1d2ec37f1108ec83a97234d47b5ac4c454cf5704200e90"}
